dataset_id: IceBridge UAF Lidar Scanner L1B Geolocated Surface Elevation Triplets V001
title: IceBridge UAF Lidar Scanner L1B Geolocated Surface Elevation Triplets V001
summary: This data set contains scanning laser altimetry data points of Alaskan glaciers and parts of East and West Antarctica acquired by the airborne University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF) Glacier Lidar system. The data were collected as part of NASA Operation IceBridge funded campaigns.
